=Description=

"n this interview, Rachel Botsman, Author of What's Mine is Yours: The Rise of Collaborative Consumption, discusses the reasons for the recent surge in investment in the sector and why the continued turbulence in global economic markets is actually helping Coll Cons businesses gain traction.

The interview was filmed at the March 2012 Collaborative Consumption summit at Nesta, which focused on new business models in the sector."


